---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Prose from "../components/Prose.astro";
---

<Layout title="Work">
  <section class="work">
    <header class="work-header">
      <Heading as="h1">Work</Heading>
    </header>
    <Prose>
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Ariel.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have spent the last twenty years exploring the craft of software development. 
      </p>
      <p>
        After studying Mathematics and Computer Science, I began as a Java developer and 
        eventually moved through roles as a team lead, product manager, and Chief Architect.
      </p>
      <p>
        A few years ago, my wife and I moved to the UK. The move coincided with the 
        start of the pandemic, which I took as an opportunity to return to the keyboard 
        and dive into areas of computing I hadn't yet explored.
      </p>

      <Heading as="h2">Recent practice</Heading>
      <p>
        Currently, I work as a freelance developer focusing on specialized client 
        projects and open-source contributions. My latest work is an AI-powered 
        transcription agent for the insurance industry; it handles the heavy lifting 
        of interview documentation so investigators can focus on the nuance of 
        case analysis.
      </p>

      <Heading as="h2">Systems architecture</Heading>
      <p>
        Before freelancing, I was a systems architect and full-stack developer at 
        Forcepoint. I joined the project in its startup phase and stayed through 
        two acquisitions, eventually redesigning the core data flow into a serverless 
        AWS architecture. I developed the prototype, trained the implementation team, 
        and guided the product's direction as a manager.
      </p>

      <Heading as="h2">The next step</Heading>
      <p>
        I am now looking to bring this perspective—of both high-level architecture 
        and hands-on build—back to a larger team where I can contribute to 
        meaningful, complex projects.
      </p>

    </Prose>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .work {
    max-width: var(--width-content);
  }

  .work-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
</style>